      "tip": "Lente = Spring. Mild and wet in Belgium."
    },
    {
      "nl": "de zomer",
      "phonetic": "duh ZOH-mer",
      "en": "Summer",
      "tip": "Long 'oh'. Belgium summers are warm but short!"
